蕾哈娜 (Rihanna) 表示，她为新专辑“找到了可以大受欢迎的东西” https://www.nme.com/news/music/rihanna-reveals-she-has-made-songs-she-could-make-hits-out-of-for-her-new-album-r9-3619627？ utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=蕾哈娜-透露她已经制作了歌曲-她可以为她的新专辑-r9制作热门歌曲Kyann-Sian WilliamsThu, 18 Apr 2024 22:02:03 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopR&B https://www.nme.com/?p=3619627 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/rihanna-@-2000-x-1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="蕾哈娜 (Rihanna) 出席 FENTY X Puma Creepers Phatty Earth Tone 派对。照片来源：Neil Mockford/WireImage" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/rihanna-@-2000-x-1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/rihanna-@-2000-x-1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/rihanna-@-2000-x-1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/rihanna-@-2000-x-1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/rihanna-@-2000-x-1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/rihanna-@-2000-x-1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我和 [A$AP] Rocky 真的很想弄清楚谁会使用什么，因为它太棒了”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rihanna-reveals-she-has-made-songs-she-could-make-hits-out-of-for-her-new-album-r9-3619627">蕾哈娜 (Rihanna) 表示她为新专辑“找到了可以制作热门歌曲的东西”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/rihanna-@-2000-x-1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="蕾哈娜 (Rihanna) 出席 FENTY X Puma Creepers Phatty Earth Tone 派对。照片来源：Neil Mockford/WireImage" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/rihanna-@-2000-x-1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/rihanna-@-2000-x-1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/rihanna-@-2000-x-1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/rihanna-@-2000-x-1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/rihanna-@-2000-x-1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/rihanna-@-2000-x-1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/rihanna">蕾哈娜 (Rihanna)</a>提供了她期待已久的新专辑的最新消息，称她“已经找到了可以制作热门歌曲的东西”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/rihanna-every-album-ranked-and-rated-2921163">蕾哈娜：每张专辑的排名和评级</a></li></ul><p>昨天（4 月 17 日），这位 Bajan 歌手出席了在伦敦举行的 FENTY x PUMA Creeper Phatty Earth Tone 鞋履系列发布会。在活动中，她向<a href="https://www.etonline.com/rihanna-reveals-biggest-hack-to-dressing-her-sons-shares-update-on-new-music-exclusive-223662" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《今夜娱乐》</em></a>谈论了她的新系列、她的时尚感和母性。</p><p>在分享<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rihanna-and-asap-rockys-second-child-is-called-riot-rose-3495102">她的儿子 RZA 和 Riot</a>最喜欢的歌曲是《Wheels On The Bus》后，蕾哈娜透露她的孩子是否会出现在她的新音乐中。</p><p> “我的意思是，这取决于他们，”这位《Needed Me》歌手说。 “我已经有了一些我觉得可以大受欢迎的东西。我和 [合作伙伴， <a href="/artists/asap-rocky">A$AP] Rocky</a>真的很想弄清楚谁会使用什么，因为它太棒了。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="蕾哈娜 (Rihanna) 表示她和 A$AP Rocky 的儿子可能会出现在未来的专辑中！ （独家的）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9lTLzGNF24c?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>本月早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rihanna-says-she-has-a-lot-of-visual-ideas-for-new-album-3615508">这位流行巨星分享了这一点<em> </em>她为备受期待的第九张专辑提出了“很多视觉创意”。</a></p><p> “这很奇怪，”她说。 “我的大脑现在正在倒退。我通常先有音乐，音乐引导我进入所有这些视觉机会，现在我拥有所有这些视觉效果，但我还没有适合它们的歌曲，但也许这就是关键，这次。也许视觉创意引导我创作出我需要创作的歌曲。”</p><p>当被问及她是否认为这个项目有点“重生”时，蕾哈娜回答说：“随意的想法，古怪的想法，与我完全无关的事情。我的意思是，我不能告诉你。对手正在注视着。”</p><p>在与<em>ET</em>交谈时，她确认她仍然“还没有”与她的视觉创意相匹配的歌曲。之后，蕾哈娜将话题从她即将推出的音乐上转移开，说道：“我不能再告诉你了。这就像我在告密我的唱片一样。”</p><p>蕾哈娜的最后一张完整专辑是她 2016 年的第八张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/anti-track-by-track-first-listen-review-11602">《Anti》。</a>自 2018 年以来，她一直在预告后续作品——名为“R9”——最初在 Instagram 评论中向粉丝承诺该作品将于明年上市。 2019年，她上传了一段狗跟着<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/house-of-pain">House Of Pain</a>的《Jump around》<a href="https://x.com/FentyStats/status/1208793427703422977?s=20">跳舞的视频，</a>并配文“更新：我自己听R9，拒绝发布”，进一步嘲讽粉丝。 </p><figure id="attachment_3619641" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3619641" style="width: 2160px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3619641" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/rihanna-@-2160x2700-1.jpg" alt="蕾哈娜 (Rihanna) 出席 FENTY X Puma Creepers Phatty Earth Tone 派对。照片来源：Neil Mockford/WireImage" width="2160" height="2700" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/rihanna-@-2160x2700-1.jpg 2160w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/rihanna-@-2160x2700-1-400x500.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/rihanna-@-2160x2700-1-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/rihanna-@-2160x2700-1-696x870.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/rihanna-@-2160x2700-1-1392x1740.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/rihanna-@-2160x2700-1-1068x1335.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2160px) 100vw, 2160px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3619641" class="wp-caption-text">蕾哈娜 (Rihanna) 出席 FENTY X Puma Creepers Phatty Earth Tone 派对。照片来源：Neil Mockford/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>然而，到了 2020 年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rihanna-tells-fans-stop-asking-about-new-album-trying-save-world-r9-2645074">她告诉歌迷不要再要求她在疫情期间发布新材料</a>，这让人们对这张专辑的希望落空了。</p><p>去年，蕾哈娜与 Live Nation 签署了一份新协议，据报道， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rihanna-is-reportedly-plan-to-release-new-music-and-go-on-tour-r9-album-3520346">这位歌手计划在未来几年的世界巡演之前发布新音乐</a>。</p><p> 12 月，蕾哈娜 (Rihanna) 进一步谣言<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rihanna-teases-new-music-and-world-tour-lets-just-blow-everything-up-3561688">，暗示可能即将推出新音乐和世界巡演</a>。 “好吧，我们总是会回去巡演。 [但是]我觉得当有新音乐出现时我想进行巡演。通过我上次巡演中演奏的歌曲，我们已经知道那会是什么。那是很久以前的事了，”她告诉<em><a href="https://www.etonline.com/rihanna-shares-how-son-rza-is-as-a-big-brother-teases-new-music-and-kids-clothing-line-exclusive" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《今晚娱乐》</a></em> 。</p><p> “我觉得我的歌迷得到他们一直在等待的东西是公平的，那就是新音乐。在那之后，让我们把一切都炸掉。”</p><p>最近， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aap-rocky-tells-fans-rihanna-is-working-on-her-ninth-album-r9-3589578">A$AP Rocky 在二月份证实蕾哈娜仍在“制作”她的第九张专辑</a>。</p><p>蕾哈娜最后发行的歌曲是 2022 年的歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rihanna-lift-me-up-new-song-black-panther-wakanda-forever-3337860">《Lift Me Up》</a> ，这是<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/black-panther-wakanda-forever">《黑豹：永远的瓦坎达》</a></em>原声带的阴郁主打单曲，也是对已故演员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chadwick-boseman">查德维克·博斯曼</a>的致敬。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rihanna-reveals-she-has-made-songs-she-could-make-hits-out-of-for-her-new-album-r9-3619627">蕾哈娜 (Rihanna) 表示她为新专辑“找到了可以制作热门歌曲的东西”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
经常与希里安·墨菲合作的史蒂芬·雷揭示了为什么“奥本海默”明星如此“特别” https://www.nme.com/news/film/frequent-cillian-murphy-collaborator-stephen-rea-reveals-why-oppenheimer-star-is-so-special-3619674?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=frequent-希里安·墨菲的合作者斯蒂芬·雷亚揭示了为什么奥本海默明星如此特别Chris EdwardsThu, 18 Apr 2024 21:27:44 +0000 Film NewsNewsChristopher NolanCillian MurphyOscars https://www.nme.com/?p=3619674 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/cillian-murphy@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/cillian-murphy@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/cillian-murphy@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/cillian-murphy@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/cillian-murphy@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/cillian-murphy@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/cillian-murphy@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “他是一个非常可爱的人”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/frequent-cillian-murphy-collaborator-stephen-rea-reveals-why-oppenheimer-star-is-so-special-3619674">经常与希里安·墨菲 (Cillian Murphy) 合作的史蒂芬·雷 (Stephen Rea) 揭示了为什么“奥本海默”明星如此“特别”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/cillian-murphy@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/cillian-murphy@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/cillian-murphy@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/cillian-murphy@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/cillian-murphy@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/cillian-murphy@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/cillian-murphy@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>爱尔兰演员斯蒂芬·雷对希<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cillian-murphy">里安·墨菲</a>大加赞赏，称这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/oppenheimer"><em>奥本海默</em></a>明星“可爱”且“非常特别”。</p><p>雷亚因在 1992 年的<em>《哭泣的游戏》</em>中的表演获得奥斯卡提名，多年来与墨菲合作了许多项目，包括<em>《冥王星上的早餐》</em>和<em>《Ballyturk》</em> 。</p><p> “他是一个非常可爱的人，”雷告诉爱尔兰新闻频道<a href="https://www.irishstar.com/culture/entertainment/cillian-murphy-labeled-something-very-32588318" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>RTE</em></a> 。 “当然，他有一些非常特别的东西，非常专注，而且他很爱笑。他是一个很好共事的人。</p><p> “他是一个非常令人愉快的人，很高兴和他一起出去喝酒等等。他对待演戏的态度非常让人放心，非常好；他了解每一个细节，而且结果如实。” </p><figure id="attachment_3619679" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3619679" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3619679" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Stephen-Rea-e1713475107481.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Stephen-Rea-e1713475107481.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Stephen-Rea-e1713475107481-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Stephen-Rea-e1713475107481-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Stephen-Rea-e1713475107481-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Stephen-Rea-e1713475107481-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Stephen-Rea-e1713475107481-1068x678.jpg 1068w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Stephen-Rea-e1713475107481-300x191.jpg 300w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Stephen-Rea-e1713475107481-768x488.jpg 768w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Stephen-Rea-e1713475107481-1536x975.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3619679" class="wp-caption-text">斯蒂芬·雷 (Stephen Rea) 与希里安·墨菲 (Cillian Murphy) 合作过多个项目。图片来源：盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>墨菲凭借在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/christopher-nolan">克里斯托弗·诺兰</a>执导的关于“原子弹之父”罗伯特·J·奥本海默的传记片《<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/oppenheimer"><em>奥本海默》</em></a>中的出色表演，获得了今年<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">奥斯卡</a>最佳男主角奖。</p><p>这部电影本身也获得了最佳影片奖，而诺兰则获得了最佳导演奖。小罗伯特·唐尼是当晚的另一位大赢家，凭借饰演反对奥本海默的美国政府官员刘易斯·施特劳斯而获得最佳男配角奖。这部电影在 2024 年颁奖典礼上总共获得了七项奥斯卡奖。</p><p>在其他新闻中，墨菲最近表示，他愿意重返<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/peaky-blinders"><em>浴血黑帮</em></a>电影中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/cillian-murpyh-totally-open-returning-peaky-blinders-film-3599557">的汤米谢尔比角色</a>。</p><p>据《 <a href="https://www.irishstar.com/culture/entertainment/cillian-murphy-peaky-blinders-movie-32108382" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>爱尔兰星报》</em></a>报道，墨菲表示他很想再次扮演这个角色，他在这部获奖剧的六季中扮演了这个角色长达十年之久。</p><p> “我总是说，如果奈特交付了一个我知道他能交付的剧本，因为他是一位如此出色的作家，我就会在那里，”这位 47 岁的人分享道。</p><p> “如果我们想看 50 岁的汤米谢尔比，我就会去那里。我们开始做吧。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/frequent-cillian-murphy-collaborator-stephen-rea-reveals-why-oppenheimer-star-is-so-special-3619674">经常与希里安·墨菲 (Cillian Murphy) 合作的史蒂芬·雷 (Stephen Rea) 揭示了为什么“奥本海默”明星如此“特别”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
活结乐队用“仅限一晚”广告牌戏弄神秘活动https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-tease-mystery-event-with-one-night-only-billboard-3619668?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=slipknot-tease-mystery-event-with-仅一晚的广告牌Max PilleyThu, 18 Apr 2024 20:41:13 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetalNu-metal https://www.nme.com/?p=3619668 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/slipknot_new_2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="活结" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/slipknot_new_2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/slipknot_new_2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/slipknot_new_2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/slipknot_new_2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/slipknot_new_2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/slipknot_new_2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>广告牌上有一个复古网站的链接，上面引用了乐队 1999 年的同名专辑</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-tease-mystery-event-with-one-night-only-billboard-3619668">活结戏弄神秘活动后的广告牌“仅限一晚”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/slipknot_new_2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="活结" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/slipknot_new_2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/slipknot_new_2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/slipknot_new_2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/slipknot_new_2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/slipknot_new_2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/slipknot_new_2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slipknot">活结乐队</a>在加利福尼亚州发布了一个神秘的广告牌，上面写着“仅限一晚”，以此来预告一场即将举行的神秘活动。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="94" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-clown-interview-tour-2024-tickets-new-material-3559353"><b>Slipknot 的 Clown 谈论 2024 年巡演和新材料：“这支乐队从未如此快乐”</b></a></li></ul><p>上周，这则明显的广告出现在通往<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/coachella">2024 年科切拉音乐节</a>的高速公路上的广告牌上，上面有乐队的标志以及第二个口号“LONG MAY YOU DIE”。</p><p>横幅上还包含<a href="https://youcantkillme.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">youcantkillme.com</a>的链接，这是一个复古网站，其中引用了乐队 1999 年的同名专辑（来自<a href="https://www.revolvermag.com/music/slipknot-tease-one-night-only-event-mysterious-desert-billboard" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>Revolver</i></a> ）。</p><p>该网站还载有乐队即将举行的演唱会日期，并附有一条说明，该页面的最新更新时间为 4 月 25 日（即下周）。总而言之，歌迷们开始猜测乐队可能正在为《Slipknot》专辑举办 25 周年纪念演出。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="活结 - 等待和流血 [官方视频] [高清]" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/B1zCN0YhW1s?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>与此同时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/could-a-new-slipknot-song-be-coming-soon-3600684">，关于乐队新音乐的谣言已经在他们的粉丝群中蔓延</a>。</p><p>新金属偶像们发行的最后一张专辑是<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/slipknot-the-end-so-far-review-3317936">《The End, So Far》</a> ，于 2022 年 8 月发行。事实证明，这是两位键盘手 Craig Jones 离开之前的最后一张完整专辑，后者于 6 月离开了乐队，还有不久后突然被踢出阵容的杰伊·温伯格（Jay Weinberg）。</p><p>从那以后，活结乐队一直<a href="https://www.nme.com/photos/music-photos/slipknot-tease-mystery-new-drummer-in-rehearsal-photo-3599624">在向粉丝们暗示新鼓手的消息，并在网上发布了一张破损的鼓槌的照片，并配上“排练”的标题。</a>然而，根据帖子的评论，乐队的现场演出似乎超出了计划。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4UOMmPxA8r/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 52